section.def:
Authority
                (監督) means the Entertainment Special Effects
            Licensing Authority established by section 3;

panel
                (委員團) means the Appeal Board panel constituted
            under section 34;

prescribed
                (訂明) means prescribed by regulations made under
                section 26;

register
                (登記冊) means the register of pyrotechnic special
            effects materials kept in accordance with section 17;

use
                (使用), in relation to special effects materials,
            includes assembling, handling, mixing, compounding, installing and discharging;
